{"contributors": null, "coordinates": null, "created_at": "Fri Mar 15 18:57:49 +0000 2019", "display_text_range": [0, 233], "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "urls": [{"display_url": "twitter.com/drpmonaghan/st\u2026", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/drpmonaghan/status/1106625803356241920", "indices": [234, 257], "url": "https://t.co/QDfOAQeQsa"}], "user_mentions": []}, "favorite_count": 63, "favorited": false, "full_text": "And this isn\u2019t just about ABA or children - it is also about inclusion, education, families, health, to name a few, and ensuring that individualized supports are available across the life course. It isn\u2019t simple or one size fits all. https://t.co/QDfOAQeQsa", "geo": null, "id": 1106630599350079500, "id_str": "1106630599350079489", "in_reply_to_screen_name": null, "in_reply_to_status_id": null, "in_reply_to_status_id_str": null, "in_reply_to_user_id": null, "in_reply_to_user_id_str": null, "is_quote_status": true, "lang": "en", "place": null, "possibly_sensitive": false, "quoted_status": {"contributors": null, "coordinates": null, "created_at": "Fri Mar 15 18:38:46 +0000 2019", "display_text_range": [17, 271], "entities": {"hashtags": [{"indices": [110, 127], "text": "ActuallyAutistic"}, {"indices": [258, 271], "text": "PausethePlan"}], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": [{"id": 2746910760, "id_str": "2746910760", "indices": [0, 16], "name": "Jonathan Weiss", "screen_name": "DrJonathanWeiss"}]}, "favorite_count": 7, "favorited": false, "full_text": "@DrJonathanWeiss 100% agree. We need all pertinent voices at the table, and this should include those who are #ActuallyAutistic. This is not a simple issue, and it\u2019s irresponsible to force a simple solution without first engaging in meaningful consultation. #PausethePlan", "geo": null, "id": 1106625803356241900, "id_str": "1106625803356241920", "in_reply_to_screen_name": "DrJonathanWeiss", "in_reply_to_status_id": 1106623680078073900, "in_reply_to_status_id_str":